{"tid":2138313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去年進入立法會後被控　梁繼平身處美國缺席聆訊　警方考慮申拘捕令","createTime":"2020-08-03T13:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T13:45:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dda708b8206a310f15ffa011533edf327eaad8c3","tid":2138313,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:28:01.000Z","msg":"港大《學苑》前總編輯梁繼平涉嫌去年 7 月 1 日，進入或逗留在立法會會議廳範圍。案件今日 (3 日) 於東區裁判法院處理，惟二人均沒有出席聆訊。控方在庭上表示，曾向兩人派遞傳票但不成功，申請押後處理案件，並提及會考慮申請拘捕令，獲裁判官批准。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被告為梁繼平 (26 歲) 及范俊文 (27 歲)，二人遭票控進入或逗留在會議廳範圍。案件今於東區裁判法院處理，二人均沒有出席聆訊。控方在庭上表示，曾向二人派遞傳票，但不成功，申請押後案件至 10 月 13 日再訊，以便警方研究如何找到兩人，及考慮是否申請拘捕令，獲裁判官何俊堯批准。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESS46507 - 46509/2019<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7-%E6%A2%81%E7%B9%BC%E5%B9%B3%E8%BA%AB%E8%99%95%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E7%94%B3%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%BB%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E7%2594%25B3%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=6b892cf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E